Kaf-ha-ya-’ayn-sad
Thikru rahmati rabbika ‘abdahu zakariyya
Ith nada rabbahu nidaan khafiyyan
Qala rabbi innee wahana al’athmu minnee waishta’ala alrra/su shayban walam akun bidu’a-ika rabbi shaqiyyan
Wa-innee khiftu almawaliya min wara-ee wakanati imraatee ‘aqiran fahab lee min ladunka waliyyan
Yarithunee wayarithu min ali ya’qooba waij’alhu rabbi radiyyan
Ya zakariyya inna nubashshiruka bighulamin ismuhu yahya lam naj’al lahu min qablu samiyyan
Qala rabbi anna yakoonu lee ghulamun wakanati imraatee ‘aqiran waqad balaghtu mina alkibari ‘itiyyan
Qala kathalika qala rabbuka huwa ‘alayya hayyinun waqad khalaqtuka min qablu walam taku shay-an
Qala rabbi ij’al lee ayatan qala ayatuka alla tukallima alnnasa thalatha layalin sawiyyan
Fakharaja ‘ala qawmihi mina almihrabi faawha ilayhim an sabbihoo bukratan wa’ashiyyan
Ya yahya khuthi alkitaba biquwwatin waataynahu alhukma sabiyyan
Wahananan min ladunna wazakatan wakana taqiyyan
Wabarran biwalidayhi walam yakun jabbaran ‘asiyyan
Wasalamun ‘alayhi yawma wulida wayawma yamootu wayawma yub’athu hayyan
Waothkur fee alkitabi maryama ithi intabathat min ahliha makanan sharqiyyan
Faittakhathat min doonihim hijaban faarsalna ilayha roohana fatamaththala laha basharan sawiyyan
Qalat innee a’oothu bialrrahmani minka in kunta taqiyyan
Qala innama ana rasoolu rabbiki li-ahaba laki ghulaman zakiyyan
Qalat anna yakoonu lee ghulamun walam yamsasnee basharun walam aku baghiyyan
Qala kathaliki qala rabbuki huwa ‘alayya hayyinun walinaj’alahu ayatan lilnnasi warahmatan minna wakana amran maqdiyyan
Fahamalat-hu faintabathat bihi makanan qasiyyan
Faajaaha almakhadu ila jith’i alnnakhlati qalat ya laytanee mittu qabla hatha wakuntu nasyan mansiyyan
Fanadaha min tahtiha alla tahzanee qad ja’ala rabbuki tahtaki sariyyan
Wahuzzee ilayki bijith’i alnnakhlati tusaqit ‘alayki rutaban janiyyan
Fakulee waishrabee waqarree ‘aynan fa-imma tarayinna mina albashari ahadan faqoolee innee nathartu lilrrahmani sawman falan okallima alyawma insiyyan
Faatat bihi qawmaha tahmiluhu qaloo ya maryamu laqad ji/ti shay-an fariyyan
Ya okhta haroona ma kana abooki imraa saw-in wama kanat ommuki baghiyyan
Faasharat ilayhi qaloo kayfa nukallimu man kana fee almahdi sabiyyan
Qala innee ‘abdu Allahi ataniya alkitaba waja’alanee nabiyyan
Waja’alanee mubarakan aynama kuntu waawsanee bialssalati waalzzakati ma dumtu hayyan
Wabarran biwalidatee walam yaj’alnee jabbaran shaqiyyan
Waalssalamu ‘alayya yawma wulidtu wayawma amootu wayawma ob’athu hayyan
Thalika ‘eesa ibnu maryama qawla alhaqqi allathee feehi yamtaroona
Ma kana lillahi an yattakhitha min waladin subhanahu itha qada amran fa-innama yaqoolu lahu kun fayakoonu
Wa-inna Allaha rabbee warabbukum fao’budoohu hatha siratun mustaqeemun
Faikhtalafa al-ahzabu min baynihim fawaylun lillatheena kafaroo min mashhadi yawmin ‘atheemin
Asmi’ bihim waabsir yawma ya/toonana lakini alththalimoona alyawma fee dalalin mubeenin
Waanthirhum yawma alhasrati ith qudiya al-amru wahum fee ghaflatin wahum la yu/minoona
Inna nahnu narithu al-arda waman ‘alayha wa-ilayna yurja’oona
Waothkur fee alkitabi ibraheema innahu kana siddeeqan nabiyyan
Ith qala li-abeehi ya abati lima ta’budu ma la yasma’u wala yubsiru wala yughnee ‘anka shay-an
Ya abati innee qad jaanee mina al’ilmi ma lam ya/tika faittabi’nee ahdika siratan sawiyyan
Ya abati la ta’budi alshshaytana inna alshshaytana kana lilrrahmani ‘asiyyan
Ya abati innee akhafu an yamassaka ‘athabun mina alrrahmani fatakoona lilshshyatani waliyyan
Qala araghibun anta ‘an alihatee ya ibraheemu la-in lam tantahi laarjumannaka waohjurnee maliyyan
Qala salamun ‘alayka saastaghfiru laka rabbee innahu kana bee hafiyyan
Waa’tazilukum wama tad’oona min dooni Allahi waad’oo rabbee ‘asa alla akoona bidu’a-i rabbee shaqiyyan
Falamma i’tazalahum wama ya’budoona min dooni Allahi wahabna lahu ishaqa waya’qooba wakullan ja’alna nabiyyan
Wawahabna lahum min rahmatina waja’alna lahum lisana sidqin ‘aliyyan
Waothkur fee alkitabi moosa innahu kana mukhlasan wakana rasoolan nabiyyan
Wanadaynahu min janibi alttoori al-aymani waqarrabnahu najiyyan
Wawahabna lahu min rahmatina akhahu haroona nabiyyan
Waothkur fee alkitabi isma’eela innahu kana sadiqa alwa’di wakana rasoolan nabiyyan
Wakana ya/muru ahlahu bialssalati waalzzakati wakana ‘inda rabbihi mardiyyan
Waothkur fee alkitabi idreesa innahu kana siddeeqan nabiyyan
Warafa’nahu makanan ‘aliyyan
Ola-ika allatheena an’ama Allahu ‘alayhim mina alnnabiyyeena min thurriyyati adama wamimman hamalna ma’a noohin wamin thurriyyati ibraheema wa-isra-eela wamimman hadayna waijtabayna itha tutla ‘alayhim ayatu alrrahmani kharroo sujjadan wabukiyyan
Fakhalafa min ba’dihim khalfun ada’oo alssalata waittaba’oo alshshahawati fasawfa yalqawna ghayyan
Illa man taba waamana wa’amila salihan faola-ika yadkhuloona aljannata wala yuthlamoona shay-an
Jannati ‘adnin allatee wa’ada alrrahmanu ‘ibadahu bialghaybi innahu kana wa’duhu ma/tiyyan
La yasma’oona feeha laghwan illa salaman walahum rizquhum feeha bukratan wa’ashiyyan
Tilka aljannatu allatee noorithu min ‘ibadina man kana taqiyyan
Wama natanazzalu illa bi-amri rabbika lahu ma bayna aydeena wama khalfana wama bayna thalika wama kana rabbuka nasiyyan
Rabbu alssamawati waal-ardi wama baynahuma fao’budhu waistabir li’ibadatihi hal ta’lamu lahu samiyyan
Wayaqoolu al-insanu a-itha ma mittu lasawfa okhraju hayyan
Awa la yathkuru al-insanu anna khalaqnahu min qablu walam yaku shay-an
Fawarabbika lanahshurannahum waalshshayateena thumma lanuhdirannahum hawla jahannama jithiyyan
Thumma lananzi’anna min kulli shee’atin ayyuhum ashaddu ‘ala alrrahmani ‘itiyyan
Thumma lanahnu a’lamu biallatheena hum awla biha siliyyan
Wa-in minkum illa wariduha kana ‘ala rabbika hatman maqdiyyan
Thumma nunajjee allatheena ittaqaw wanatharu alththalimeena feeha jithiyyan
Wa-itha tutla ‘alayhim ayatuna bayyinatin qala allatheena kafaroo lillatheena amanoo ayyu alfareeqayni khayrun maqaman waahsanu nadiyyan
Wakam ahlakna qablahum min qarnin hum ahsanu athathan wari/yan
Qul man kana fee alddalalati falyamdud lahu alrrahmanu maddan hatta itha raaw ma yoo’adoona imma al’athaba wa-imma alssa’ata fasaya’lamoona man huwa sharrun makanan waad’afu jundan
Wayazeedu Allahu allatheena ihtadaw hudan waalbaqiyatu alssalihatu khayrun ‘inda rabbika thawaban wakhayrun maraddan
Afaraayta allathee kafara bi-ayatina waqala laootayanna malan wawaladan
Attala’a alghayba ami ittakhatha ‘inda alrrahmani ‘ahdan
Kalla sanaktubu ma yaqoolu wanamuddu lahu mina al’athabi maddan
Wanarithuhu ma yaqoolu waya/teena fardan
Waittakhathoo min dooni Allahi alihatan liyakoonoo lahum ‘izzan
Kalla sayakfuroona bi’ibadatihim wayakoonoona ‘alayhim diddan
Alam tara anna arsalna alshshayateena ‘ala alkafireena taozzuhum azzan
Fala ta’jal ‘alayhim innama na’uddu lahum ‘addan
Yawma nahshuru almuttaqeena ila alrrahmani wafdan
Wanasooqu almujrimeena ila jahannama wirdan
La yamlikoona alshshafa’ata illa mani ittakhatha ‘inda alrrahmani ‘ahdan
Waqaloo ittakhatha alrrahmanu waladan
Laqad ji/tum shay-an iddan
Takadu alssamawatu yatafattarna minhu watanshaqqu al-ardu watakhirru aljibalu haddan
An da’aw lilrrahmani waladan
Wama yanbaghee lilrrahmani an yattakhitha waladan
In kullu man fee alssamawati waal-ardi illa atee alrrahmani ‘abdan
Laqad ahsahum wa’addahum ‘addan
Wakulluhum ateehi yawma alqiyamati fardan
Inna allatheena amanoo wa’amiloo alssalihati sayaj’alu lahumu alrrahmanu wuddan
Fa-innama yassarnahu bilisanika litubashshira bihi almuttaqeena watunthira bihi qawman luddan
Wakam ahlakna qablahum min qarnin hal tuhissu minhum min ahadin aw tasma’u lahum rikzan